%^BOLD%^-=%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Mentalism Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Clerics with the mentalism domain use superior strategy and tactics to determine, subvert and dismantly their opponents' plans before they ever come to fruition.

Clerics with the Mentalism Domain gain the following benefits:
- A +1 caster level bonus when casting abjuration sphere spells.

The mentalism domain contains the following spells:

Mind Fog, Trace Teleport, Greater Dispel Magic, Inner Eye, Mind Blank

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Cevahir

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
